# Earth Blue Marble Texture

This file is a placeholder for the Earth texture.

To add a proper Earth texture:
1. Download a free Earth texture from NASA's Blue Marble collection
2. Save it as earth-blue-marble.jpg in this directory
3. The texture will be automatically loaded by the SimpleEarth component

Alternative sources:
- NASA Visible Earth: https://visibleearth.nasa.gov/collection/1484/blue-marble
- Natural Earth: https://www.naturalearthdata.com/